trucks trailor tipped pulling the truck with it, he quickly transformed and losing 
his balance smashed his head into a tree... "Gah!" Shaking his head he looked 
back at the others. "I'll be back... and when i do i will drink the energon I 
squeeze from your innards." He stood holding his head and pulling the wrecked 
prime helmet off he began running towards the direction maxima disseapered 
to...
